<div class="Box-body">
  <p class="mb-2">
    <strong><%= domain.domain %></strong> is the only verified/approved
    domain in the <strong><%= domain.owner.to_param %></strong> enterprise.
    Because at least one verified or approved domain
    is required to restrict email notifications to domain emails, unverifying this domain may
    disable restrictions for member organizations.
  </p>

  <p class="color-fg-danger">
    <strong>
      Deleting this domain may allow members to receive notifications at any email address for any associated organizations which had enabled notification restrictions,
      but had not verified or approved any additional domains.
    </strong>
  </p>
</div>


<div class="Box-footer">
  <%= button_to "Unverify this domain and disable notification restrictions", unverify_stafftools_domain_path(domain.id),
      class: "btn btn-danger btn-block mt-2",
      method: :put %>
</div>
